item.title: LYFT
item.description: score:43 Chances: Lyft, Inc. has been making significant strides under new CEO David Risher, improving on costs and execution. The company is benefiting from positive fundamentals in the ridesharing industry and gaining traction in becoming a leaner and more efficient company. The potential for a partnership between Lyft and DoorDash could be a positive development for both companies.
